Package: SpatialDryArtifacts
Title: Edge Dryspot Detection for Spatial Transcriptomics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jiali", "He", email = "jhe46@jh.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Stephanie", "Hicks", role = "ctb", comment = "PI"),
    person("Michael", "Totty", role = "ctb"),
    person("Jacqui", "Benefiel", role = "ctb"))
Description: Implements enhanced methods for detecting edge dryspots and technical 
    artifacts in spatial transcriptomics data. Provides spatially-aware quality 
    control algorithms for Visium and other spatial platforms, extending the 
    SpotSweeper framework with raster-based edge detection capabilities.
